name: $category
desc: Returns: Code to identify the general type of benefits under which products and services are provided.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Code to identify the general type of benefits under which products and services are provided.

name: $excluded
desc: Returns: True if the indicated class of service is excluded from the plan, missing or False indicates the product or service is included in the coverage.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: True if the indicated class of service is excluded from the plan, missing or False indicates the product or service is included in the coverage.

name: $::name
desc: Returns: A short name or tag for the benefit.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A short name or tag for the benefit.

name: $description
desc: Returns: A richer description of the benefit or services covered.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A richer description of the benefit or services covered.

name: $network
desc: Returns: Is a flag to indicate whether the benefits refer to in-network providers or out-of-network providers.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Is a flag to indicate whether the benefits refer to in-network providers or out-of-network providers.

name: $unit
desc: Returns: Indicates if the benefits apply to an individual or to the family.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicates if the benefits apply to an individual or to the family.

name: $term
desc: Returns: The term or period of the values such as 'maximum lifetime benefit' or 'maximum annual visits'.
